OL,3,CWater company bosses face ban on
OL,4,Cbonuses over illegal sewage spills
OL,6,FWater company bosses are facing a ban
OL,7,Fon bonuses over illegal sewage spills,
OL,8,FITV News West of England reporter
OL,9,FSangita Lal reports from Exmouth
OL,11,FBosses of water companies which have
OL,12,Fillegally spilled sewage face a ban on
OL,13,Ftheir bonuses.
OL,15,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Barclay is
OL,16,Fset to block payouts to executives of
OL,17,Ffirms which are polluting rivers,
OL,18,Flakes and seas, starting with bonuses
OL,19,Fin the 2024-25 financial year from
OL,20,FApril.
