OL,3,CWater company bosses face ban on
OL,4,Cbonuses over illegal sewage spills
OL,6,FCampaigners, Labour and the Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrats have been calling for the
OL,8,Fpolicy amid outrage at bosses
OL,9,Fpocketing more than #26 million in
OL,10,Fbonuses, benefits and incentives over
OL,11,Fthe last four years.
OL,13,FSenior executives from five of the 11
OL,14,Fwater companies that deal with sewage
OL,15,Ftook bonuses last year, while the
OL,16,Fother six said they declined after
OL,17,Fpublic anger.
OL,19,FRegulator Ofwat will consult on
OL,20,Fdetails of the proposed ban later this
OL,21,Fyear.
