OL,3,CWater company bosses face ban on
OL,4,Cbonuses over illegal sewage spills
OL,6,FCausing significant pollution at a
OL,7,Fbathing site or conservation area, or
OL,8,Fwhere a company has been found guilty
OL,9,Fof serious management failings, is
OL,10,Flikely to lead to a punishment,
OL,11,Faccording to the Department for
OL,12,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs.
OL,14,FThe development comes as water
OL,15,Fcompanies could be fined up to a 10%
OL,16,Fof their turnover for poor customer
OL,17,Fservice, under new powers given to
OL,18,FOfwat.
