OL,3,CWater company bosses face ban on
OL,4,Cbonuses over illegal sewage spills
OL,6,FOfwat said there are too many
OL,7,Finstances where customers feel let
OL,8,Fdown and their supplier does not have
OL,9,Ftheir best interests at heart, after a
OL,10,Ffall in satisfaction across most of
OL,11,Fthe companies.
OL,13,FThe regulator already has the power to
OL,14,Fblock companies paying out money to
OL,15,Fshareholders if they fail to meet
OL,16,Fperformance standards, and can impose
OL,17,Ffines.
