OL,3,CWater company bosses face ban on
OL,4,Cbonuses over illegal sewage spills
OL,6,FA separate report by the Consumer
OL,7,FCouncil for Water (CCW) in September
OL,8,Ffound that Southern Water was the most
OL,9,Fcomplained-about company, with three
OL,10,Ftimes higher than average.
OL,12,FComplaints received by Southern Water
OL,13,Fwere almost three times higher than
OL,14,Fthe overall average for water and
OL,15,Fsewerage companies, while Thames
OL,16,FWater's were just over one-and-a-half
OL,17,Ftimes higher.
OL,19,FMore than 230,000 complaints were made
OL,20,Fto water companies in England and
OL,21,FWales by households in 2022 to 2023.
