OL,3,CWater company bosses face ban on
OL,4,Cbonuses over illegal sewage spills
OL,6,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Barclay
OL,7,Fsaid: "We expect water companies to
OL,8,Fensure customers are properly
OL,9,Fsupported when services are disrupted.
OL,11,F"Enforcement action for poor customer
OL,12,Fservice is an important and necessary
OL,13,Fstep to restoring trust in the water
OL,14,Fsector and has been made possible
OL,15,Fthanks to government giving Ofwat
OL,16,Fincreased powers to modify the
OL,17,Flicences of companies in England under
OL,18,Fthe Environment Act.
