OL,6,F"We are driving forward more
OL,7,Finvestment, stronger regulation and
OL,8,Ftougher enforcement through the Plan
OL,9,Ffor Water and will continue working
OL,10,Fclosely with regulators to improve
OL,11,Foutcomes for both customers and the
OL,12,Fenvironment."
OL,14,FPreviously, Ofwat announced to #473 a
OL,15,Fyear from April 1.
OL,17,FMoney raised from the hike will fund
OL,18,Finvestment in infrastructure to reduce
OL,19,Fthe amount of sewage being spilled in
OL,20,Fthe country's rivers and seas.
