OL,6,FA spokesperson for Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,7,FWater said: "Ofwat last year
OL,8,Frecognised the level of alignment of
OL,9,FWelsh Water remuneration awards to
OL,10,Fdelivery for customers and the
OL,11,Fenvironment and urged other companies
OL,12,Fto aspire to such levels.
OL,14,F"The executive directors also decided
OL,15,Fto forego their annual variable pay
OL,16,Fawards for the year. We will review
OL,17,FOfwat's consultation and respond in
OL,18,Fdue course."
